Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.28,0:00:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With the Millennium Puzzle complete,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.91,0:00:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The young boy Yugi Mutou became a master of the Dark Games.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He was challenged by a person that has a Millennium Item like him,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.16,0:00:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the owner of the Millennium Eye, Pegasus, and went to the Duelist Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.83,0:00:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To save the soul of Sugoroku, that was stolen by him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.93,0:00:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Together with his friends and with his other self.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.33,0:00:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A magazine page I can't finish reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.21,0:00:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to read it, but somehow I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.07,0:00:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Game software is stacked in the corner of the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.85,0:01:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't play them, will they become meaningless?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.78,0:01:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just beyond the table, and I'm trying to talk with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.60,0:01:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A never changing facial expression is on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.92,0:01:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I'm right here with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.17,0:01:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They can't reach, they can't reach, these feelings of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.97,0:01:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what's really important?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.25,0:01:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go, Yugi!\NIt's time to determine the strongest!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.73,0:01:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,DUEL!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.49,0:01:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trap Card, activate!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.69,0:02:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Lamp!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.27,0:02:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.64,0:02:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The lamp deflects your attack\Nat your {\i1}own{\i0} Monster!{\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.22,0:02:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba! To trap {\i1}me{\i0}...\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.42,0:02:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\bord1\i1}Yugi, the {\i1\b1}real{\i0\b0} trap I've set for you\Nis just {\i1\b1}beginning{\i0\b0}..!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.76,0:02:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The heart of the world's {\i1\b1}strongest{\i0\b0} Monster\Nhas already begun to beat in my hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.13,0:02:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right...\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.80,0:02:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm going to {\i1\b1}fuse{\i0\b0} 3 Blue-Eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.62,0:02:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Strongest! The Magnificent!\N Blue-Eyes Ultimate Dragon"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.55,0:02:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.78,0:02:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi-kun fell into Kaiba-kun's trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.02,0:02:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's pretty good!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.59,0:02:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The match just started!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.69,0:02:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Do your best, other Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.53,0:03:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still the first half. They're\Njust testing each other to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.64,0:03:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The real fight starts now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.61,0:03:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaiba! It's time we settled our scores!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.41,0:03:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I {\b1}will{\b0} defeat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.61,0:03:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I already have one Blue-Eyes White Dragon.\NWhen I get three, my victory is set.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.55,0:03:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My plan is to fuse 3 Blue-Eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.59,0:03:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Strong! {\alphaFF}Invincible! Ultimate!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.38,0:03:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Strong! Invincible! {\alphaFF}Ultimate!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.05,0:03:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Strong! Invincible! Ultimate!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.43,0:03:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi, when you add this formula\N there's only one answer...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.43,0:03:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And that is your{\b1} loss{\b0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.65,0:03:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come! It's my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.74,0:03:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got my trump card, Undo Magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.81,0:03:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll play this card with La Jinn.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.58,0:03:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I play La Jinn the Genie\N of the Lamp once again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.45,0:04:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I destroy one Magic Card on\Nyour side of the board!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.61,0:04:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.40,0:04:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A good card was stricken.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.24,0:04:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sealing Swords of Light stops all monsters\Nfrom attacking for 3 full turns.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.64,0:04:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card is hard to beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.20,0:04:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.73,0:04:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can Yugi-kun defeat that combo with\NLa Jinn and Magic Lamp?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.14,0:04:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's alright! There's got to be a way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.69,0:04:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Good. I drew the Magic Box card.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.51,0:04:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The combo that will destroy La Jinn and Magic Lamp is finished!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.28,0:04:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.86,0:04:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now! Come on and attack La Jinn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.26,0:04:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you'll just fall into my trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.50,0:05:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll break the La Jinn and \NMagic Lamp combo, Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.27,0:05:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Card, The Eye Of Truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.14,0:05:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Eye Of Truth...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.81,0:05:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Magic Card lets me see\Nall the cards in your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.75,0:05:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.08,0:05:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba has a Blue-Eyes in his hand...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.32,0:05:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.55,0:05:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Kaiba bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.91,0:05:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew he had a Blue-Eyes up his sleeves!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.86,0:05:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's still 2 left in his deck...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.93,0:05:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}3{\i0} Blue-Eyes...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.40,0:05:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't realize his deck was {\i1}that{\i0} powerful...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.17,0:05:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! He can beat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.63,0:05:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's beaten them before!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.40,0:05:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.32,0:05:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why isn't Kaiba attacking\Nwith his Blue-Eyes...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.01,0:05:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Cursed Yugi...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.17,0:05:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Exposing my cards is the\Nultimate humiliation...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.45,0:05:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My plan is to fuse 3 Blue-Eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.05,0:05:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In order to do so, the condition\Nis that I have the Fusion card.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.56,0:06:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll surely fuse all 3 Blue-Eyes White Dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.63,0:06:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll return the humiliation you handed to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.53,0:06:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's it...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.76,0:06:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I were Kaiba, I'd try to fuse\Nthe 3 Blue-Eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.33,0:06:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's no doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.30,0:06:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His plan is to fuse all 3 Blue-Eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.11,0:06:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But right now, I don't even have a card\Nstrong enough to beat {\b1}one{\b0} Blue-Eyes...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.81,0:06:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}First I have to break Kaiba's combo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.78,0:06:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Box!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.72,0:06:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.86,0:06:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Box destroys one magic combo\Nmade by the opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.43,0:06:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the other box, Magic Lamp\Nis sacrificed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.97,0:06:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-my Magic Lamp...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.58,0:06:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now come out, Black Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.82,0:07:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Magic!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.29,0:07:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,La Jinn is beaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.04,0:07:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Bastard....!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.13,0:07:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.88,0:07:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you fuse 3 Blue-Eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.57,0:07:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take your Life Points to 0\Nbefore that happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.54,0:07:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the Yugi I know!\NYou know me well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.85,0:07:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't underestimate me, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.01,0:07:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My formula for victory is more\Nperfect than you realize!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.55,0:07:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your total loss is close at hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.26,0:07:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But before that, I'll show you\Nsomething exciting...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.13,0:07:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.08,0:07:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.43,0:07:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll show you the most terrifying combo\Nthat exists on this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.00,0:07:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is the ultimate murder combo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.00,0:07:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Saggi the Dark Clown in Defense Mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.24,0:07:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I set another card in the Sub Stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.22,0:08:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.42,0:08:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Saggi's Defense is 1500...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.02,0:08:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Black Magician can easily beat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.75,0:08:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.05,0:08:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't help but feel something's wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.46,0:08:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.43,0:08:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You have no choice but\Nto attack Saggi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.50,0:08:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, until he attacks, I'll keep\Nplaying Saggi until he's forced to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.34,0:08:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You are caught in a trap of {\b1}Hell{\b0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.41,0:08:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.68,0:08:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Good card.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.48,0:08:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dark Knight Gaia...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.45,0:08:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gaia beat Saggi in our last fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.99,0:08:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! I change my Main Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.49,0:08:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Knight Gaia to battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.76,0:08:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack Saggi!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:00.95,0:09:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spiral Shaver!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.01,0:09:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saggi the Dark Clown is beaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.64,0:09:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fell for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.87,0:09:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.29,0:09:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Knight Gaia!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.42,0:09:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not just Gaia!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.85,0:09:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Magician too...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.02,0:09:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.78,0:09:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.16,0:09:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deck Destruction Virus of Death!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.00,0:09:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.38,0:09:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I infected Saggi the Dark Clown\Nwith the Death Virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.23,0:09:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The second your monster attacked Saggi
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.32,0:09:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it was infected by the virus!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.79,0:09:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deck Destruction Virus of Death will spread\Nto every card in your deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.01,0:09:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not good!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.60,0:09:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Virus card's effect...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.90,0:10:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,destroys all monsters with 1500\NAttack Points or greater!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.37,0:10:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just destroyed your whole deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.96,0:10:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.93,0:10:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With that worthless deck you've got left,\Nall you can do is wait quietly for defeat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.57,0:10:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, this time I'll teach you what a\NDuel of terror is all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.87,0:10:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That damn bastard Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.08,0:10:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using such a ridiculous card...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.64,0:10:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's Yugi going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.21,0:10:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi-kun can only use low-Attack monsters\Nand Magic cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.79,0:10:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that Kaiba has 3 Blue-Eyes in his hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.89,0:10:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.40,0:11:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sucks for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.63,0:11:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The runner of Kaiba Corporation's not too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.47,0:11:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With all his strong monsters gone,\N Yugi's like a chicken with no wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.51,0:11:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's see what he'll do next.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.68,0:11:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.25,0:11:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we both have no monsters in play.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.48,0:11:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw a card and set them on your disk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.29,0:11:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, my monsters will slaughter\Nyours in a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.59,0:11:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The card I drew is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.86,0:11:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Demon's Summon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.60,0:11:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Its Attack Points exceed 1500.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.53,0:11:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if I play it, it'll just vanish.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.97,0:11:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.50,0:11:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before you play your next card, \NI'll pass and wait patiently.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.18,0:11:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All I can do now is play Silver Fang in Defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.42,0:12:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All you have left is junk designed to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.36,0:12:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The second Blue-Eyes White Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.50,0:12:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi, keep running and playing your\Nweakling monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.00,0:12:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In the end, I'll collect the Fusion Card\Nand the third Blue-Eyes White Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.58,0:12:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And Ill fuse the 3 Blue-Eyes \Ninto the ultimate monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.38,0:12:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Until that time, I have to save the\NBlue-Eyes cards in the Sub Card Stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.56,0:12:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minotaur in Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.79,0:12:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut off Silver Fang's head!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.47,0:12:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Axe Crusher!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.77,0:12:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silver Fang is beaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.71,0:12:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit! Can't he do {\i1}anything{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.94,0:13:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The other Yugi has won every time up until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.78,0:13:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He won't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.28,0:13:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still have much {\i1}stronger{\i0} monsters in reserve!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.59,0:13:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even if I stick with Minotaur...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.06,0:13:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the strongest monster you have\Nis no match against him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.06,0:13:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now Yugi! It's your turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.13,0:13:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's no use...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.17,0:13:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Forget {\i1\b1}Blue-Eyes{\i0\b0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.70,0:13:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't even have a card \Nthat can beat {\i1\b1}Minotaur{\i0\b0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.27,0:13:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, go ahead and play your card.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.51,0:13:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well, it'll just be another measly\NDefense monster won't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.91,0:13:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Anyway, all I can do is draw a card...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.61,0:13:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I won't give up until my Life Points reach 0!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.69,0:13:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Griffor card!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.72,0:13:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! I use this card!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.63,0:13:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Griffor!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.07,0:13:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Griffor?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.44,0:14:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another weak monster in Defense Mode?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.61,0:14:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Minotaur will crush it in an instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.68,0:14:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Griffor is not in Defense Mode, Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.05,0:14:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.45,0:14:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Horn of the Unicorn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.35,0:14:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I combo attack with this card!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.22,0:14:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Griffor Arrow!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.16,0:14:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minotaur is beaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.63,0:14:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good going! Scared {\i1}now{\i0}, Kaiba?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.47,0:14:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.84,0:14:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Yugi-kun's turn to show his ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.51,0:14:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're counting on you, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.08,0:14:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for killing off that weak Minotaur.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.91,0:14:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've now left yourself wide open\Nfor the rest of this turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.59,0:14:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.96,0:14:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now I have 3 Blue-Eyes White Dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.23,0:14:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, I play this Magic Card from my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.16,0:15:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Holy Elf's Blessing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.45,0:15:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Holy Elf's Blessing's effect\Nincreases my Life by 300 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.65,0:15:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Did Kaiba lure me into attacking Minotaur\Nbecause he knew he had Holy Elf's Blessing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.89,0:15:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was to get my monster into Attack Mode...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.67,0:15:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This turn, I'll play one of the Blue-Eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.40,0:15:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To fuse all 3 will take another turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.87,0:15:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You'll be at my mercy soon, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.58,0:15:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth, Blue-Eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.85,0:16:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.10,0:16:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.86,0:16:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Burst Stream of Destruction!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.19,0:16:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The trash monster's been killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.96,0:16:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Life will vanish soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.27,0:16:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, it's your turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.14,0:16:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Giant Soldier of Stone in Defense Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.31,0:16:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn over!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.61,0:16:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.22,0:16:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi.... since the first match we had, I've tasted a hunger for victory that was never satisfied...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.33,0:17:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I can finally satisfy this hunger!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.03,0:17:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This pain....
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.69,0:17:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'LL LET YOU FEEL IT!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.32,0:17:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,BLUE-EYES ULTIMATE DRAGON!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.36,0:17:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Th-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.18,0:17:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the fusion of 3 Blue-Eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.46,0:17:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.63,0:17:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Yugi...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.67,0:17:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the strongest killing machine!\NThe ultimate form of monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.84,0:17:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fusion of 3 Blue-Eyes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.74,0:17:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}4500{\i0} Attack Points?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.74,0:17:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.45,0:17:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-kun's real plan was to\Ncreate this Ultimate Dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.42,0:18:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This match's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.42,0:18:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No miracle will save him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.79,0:18:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Goddess of Victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.76,0:18:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Save Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.30,0:18:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Blue-Eyes Ultimate Dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.10,0:18:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What can I do against an enemy\Nwith 4500 Attack Points...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.48,0:18:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And my Life Points are almost gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.18,0:18:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have no cards that can fight\Nagainst the Ultimate Dragon...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.58,0:18:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.38,0:18:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's now {\i1}your{\i0} turn to carry the\Ncross of defeat like I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.22,0:18:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you'll crawl on the ground in shame!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.93,0:18:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come! Blue-Eyes Ultimate Dragon, attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.67,0:18:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ultimate Burst!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.21,0:18:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My victory is set.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.76,0:19:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If this continues, I'll lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.80,0:19:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now Yugi! It's your turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.25,0:19:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want to surrender, draw a card!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.89,0:19:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.93,0:19:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.32,0:19:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, don't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.02,0:19:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our goal is to get into Pegasus' castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.69,0:19:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's right in front of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.73,0:19:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you give up now, we'll never walk through those doors!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.71,0:19:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Grandpa...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.81,0:19:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.12,0:19:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.62,0:19:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Come at me until the very end!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.42,0:19:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi! I want to crush you\Nat your maximum strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.09,0:20:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Anyway, if I can't survive\Nthe next turn, I lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.20,0:20:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This turn determines the match!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.14,0:20:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.07,0:20:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.01,0:20:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.08,0:20:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,YUGI!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.38,0:20:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's useless! No matter what card\Nyou draw, it's hopeless!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.55,0:20:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I bet my life...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.42,0:20:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ON THIS CARD!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.12,0:20:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(137,135)}"Preview"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.46,0:20:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi is able to come back\Nafter being in a desperate pinch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.40,0:20:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! You can get rid\Nof Kaiba-kun's Ultimate Dragon!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.97,0:20:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Kaiba-kun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.67,0:20:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous to walk backwards\Nlike that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.28,0:20:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When your Life Points hit 0,\Nyou'll walk off the ledge?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.75,0:20:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,NO WAY!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.51,0:20:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: {\c&HFCFFEB&}"Kuriboh Multiplies!\NThe Astonishing Conclusion"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.45,0:20:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel Standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.14,0:21:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The flask shines bright
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.38,0:21:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}waiting in the Science Lab
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.75,0:21:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}By rubbing our cold hands together...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.99,0:21:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They will become warm
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.72,0:21:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}An energy shower
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.30,0:21:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It'll shower all over you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.36,0:21:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I will support your lonely back
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.58,0:21:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}An energy shower
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.56,0:21:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're not alone
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.22,0:22:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Because you're surrounded by a ring of friendship
